      #c09df5  effectColor from game palette → purple circle fill
      #7744bb  saturated purple              → circle outline stroke
      #e63e3e                               → red puck ring + stem (outer)
      #f59da0  highPlayerLight from palette  → red puck interior fill
      #3ea7e6                               → blue puck ring + stem (outer)
